    "Id": 13,
    "link": "/my-blog/13",
    "title": "This is the title",
    "date": "01/01/2000",
    "type": "blog",
    "html": "<h2>This is the title</h2>\n<h2>01/01/2000</h2>\n<p>This is the directory where my custom workflow will commit and pr new blogs into the app.\nDoing it this way to not incur a lot of charges for cloud sql since this is literally a personal website there is no need for it to cost me more than 5 bucks a month</p>\n<p>all obby parsing can be done on entry to a blog item, just no api calls</p>\n<p>all links must be valid so the workflow must also contain a list of links and alert the developer on publish if their link will not work\neventually in the future maybe add it so it creates a node automatically, but i think i will leave that for tektite, this is a personal portfolio after all\n<a href=\"/Blog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Blog</a></p>\n",
    "LinksTo": [
      "Blog"
    ]
